<h1>The Hexmap</h1>
<p>For this campaign, I'm making use of a hex maps for exploration. Instead of trying to keep track of everything in miles, I'm instead rewriting things so that travel is represented in hexes per day.</p>
<p>While traveling, you'll want to keep the following in mind:</p>
<ul>
    <li>A party of adventurer can explore four hexes in a day.</li>
    <li> Some hexes take longer to traverse, and may come with special considerations.</li>
    <li>I'll be populating the map with stuff to find, so don't hesitate to explore!</li>
</ul>
